                        <li>Company Size: 500-5,000 employees</li>
                        <li>Annual Revenue: $50M - $500M+</li>
                        <li>Industry: Mid-market to Enterprise Retail, B2B, Manufacturing</li>
                        <li>Growth Stage: Scale-up to Mature Enterprise</li>
                        <li>Geographic Focus: North America, Europe, APAC</li>
                    </ul>

                    <strong>Technology Profile:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Current Platform: Legacy systems, outgrowing current solution</li>
                        <li>Tech Stack: Advanced integration needs</li>
                        <li>IT Budget: $1M+ annually</li>
                        <li>Development Resources: In-house technical teams</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="subsection">
                <div class="subsection-title">Buyer Personas</div>
                
