                    <strong>Pain Points:</strong> Platform scalability, technical debt, integration complexity<br>
                    <strong>Success Metrics:</strong> System uptime, performance optimization, cost efficiency
                </div>

                <div class="buyer-persona">
                    <div class="persona-title">Technical Buyer: Director of E-commerce</div>
                    <strong>Demographics:</strong> 30-45 years old, e-commerce specialist background<br>
                    <strong>Pain Points:</strong> Conversion optimization, customer experience, feature limitations<br>
                    <strong>Success Metrics:</strong> Conversion rates, average order value, customer satisfaction
                </div>

                <div class="buyer-persona">
                    <div class="persona-title">Financial Stakeholder: CFO / Finance Director</div>
